item.title: Trump says 'Too Late' Powell must lower interest rates after weak ADP jobs report
item.description: Trump has branded Powell with the nickname "Too Late" as a criticism of the Fed Chair's continuing decision to hold interest rates steady.

item.title: Government collapse plunges Netherlands in turmoil ahead of key NATO summit
item.description: Right-wing leader Geert Wilders' exit from government ended the already fragile Dutch coalition after just 11 months in power.

item.title: Supreme Court rules Trump can revoke protected status for 500,000 immigrants pending appeal
item.description: The Supreme Court's decision affects immigrants from Cuba, Haiti, Nicaragua, and Venezuela who had fled their conflict-ridden countries.

item.title: '130 days of Elon Musk': Report cites more than 100 times DOGE boss benefited self, business
